    "This project is open source. Contributions are welcome. Feel free to open an issue ticket and discuss new features.\n[Source Code](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [License](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [Issue tracker](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**Dependencies**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dieses Projekt ist Open Source. Beiträge sind willkommen. Erstelle gerne ein Issue-Ticket und diskutiere neue Funktionen.\n[Quellcode](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [Lizenz](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [Issue-Tracker](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**Abhängigkeiten**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ce projet est open source. Les contributions sont les bienvenues. N'hésitez pas à ouvrir un ticket et à discuter de nouvelles fonctionnalités.\n[Code source](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [Licence](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [Suivi des problèmes](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**Dépendances**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Este proyecto es de código abierto. Las contribuciones son bienvenidas. No dude en abrir un ticket y discutir nuevas funcionalidades.\n[Código fuente](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [Licencia](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [Seguimiento de problemas](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**Dependencias**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このプロジェクトはオープンソースです。貢献を歓迎します。お気軽にイシューを作成して新機能について議論してください。\n[ソースコード](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [ライセンス](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [イシュートラッカー](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**依存関係**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本项目是开源的，欢迎贡献。欢迎提交问题并讨论新功能。\n[源代码](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [许可证](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [问题追踪](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**依赖**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Este projeto é de código aberto. Contribuições são bem-vindas. Sinta-se à vontade para abrir um ticket e discutir novas funcionalidades.\n[Código fonte](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [Licença](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [Rastreador de problemas](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**Dependências**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 프로젝트는 오픈 소스입니다. 기여를 환영합니다. 이슈를 열어 새로운 기능에 대해 자유롭게 논의해 주세요.\n[소스 코드](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels), [라이선스](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/blob/main/LICENSE), [이슈 트래커](https://github.com/philipparndt/iot-panels/issues)\n\n**종속성**\n[CocoaMQTT](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will delete all demo dashboards, data sources, and widgets, then recreate them.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alle Demo-Dashboards, Datenquellen und Widgets werden gelöscht und neu erstellt."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tous les tableaux de bord, sources de données et widgets de démonstration seront supprimés puis recréés."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto eliminará todos los dashboards, fuentes de datos y widgets de demostración, y los recreará."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "すべてのデモダッシュボード、データソース、ウィジェットを削除して再作成します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这将删除所有演示仪表板、数据源和小组件，然后重新创建。"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Isso excluirá todos os painéis, fontes de dados e widgets de demonstração e os recriará."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "모든 데모 대시보드, 데이터 소스 및 위젯을 삭제하고 다시 생성합니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will permanently delete this home and all its dashboards, data sources, and widgets.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dieses Zuhause wird dauerhaft gelöscht, einschließlich aller Dashboards, Datenquellen und Widgets."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cette maison sera définitivement supprimée, y compris tous ses tableaux de bord, sources de données et widgets."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto eliminará permanentemente esta casa y todos sus dashboards, fuentes de datos y widgets."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このホームとすべてのダッシュボード、データソース、ウィジェットが完全に削除されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
